Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.72,0:00:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he is the Punishment Bearer, Akihisa\NYoshii's Being is used for special purposes.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.85,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It possesses prodigious strength in addition to being corporeal.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me the world map.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, he is treated as the teachers' gofers.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, take the tables to the auditorium.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, take down the soccer goal.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always have to do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Punishment Bearer, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, this pisses me off!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.92,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain that the Bearer's Being feels will be transmitted back to its owner.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a quiz coming up. Make sure you review the material.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll {\i1}review{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.81,0:00:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Sunday, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to study at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.18,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the weekend, but class F is \Nrequired to take supplementary lessons.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yoshii... What happened to your clothes?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I went to {\i1}review{\i0}...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you got your ass kicked, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.17,0:03:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm particularly hungry today, since I was forcibly enslaved and all...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Being seems like it would be pretty convenient to have, but I guess not, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouko? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't have lessons today, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to do a little self-studying.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's Sunday as long as you're here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to come.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come if you won't come, even if it's a school day.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.15,0:03:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought your own lunch today, right, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1/67th of a cup ramen.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1/67th?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.48,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of half of half of half of half of half.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 1/64th, dude.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you suck at fractions.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff's not bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be bawling if that were my lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.47,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V-very well! I'll just have to share my lunch with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made too much and forgot to take it out.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'd be a waste to trash it, so you want it?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One sec.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I left it at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, and I spent all that time on it...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.94,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my bad. I almost believed that you had\Ndone something feminine for a second there!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my neck is going to break!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.23,0:04:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! I forgot to bring it!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.19,0:04:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-almost...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys never quit.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... is this class F, the one full of idiots?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Hazuki?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.72,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.51,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Akihisa. I had no idea the entire country knew you were such a dumbass.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't it just be the neighborhood!?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! You really are Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on... Why do you know Aki, Hazuki?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my husband.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.19,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out with him because we're going to get married!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa had indeed met Hazuki before.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll explore the details later.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, Aki? What have you done to my sister!?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for an inquisition.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.69,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defendant Yoshii Akihisa is charged with breaking the FFF's blood pact.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.75,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He perpetrated a felony by going out with a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections, correct?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defendant, any last words?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't my defense come before my last words!?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verdict is guilty. Death penalty.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What grade are you in?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifth.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way more mature than Akihisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Pretty over there!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you come here today?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.18,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! You left this at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lunches! Thanks a ton, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.79,0:06:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you brought both of them...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to cook.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see what's going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.55,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you were acting so serious\Nfirst thing in the morning. You even woke up early.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to make-
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a little strange...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you made a lunch especially for Akihisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.81,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'd die before I did that!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what exactly where you acting so serious over?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not lunch, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing! A model!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A model?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1:35 King Tiger!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A German heavy tank...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in luck, bro.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than your 1/64th of a cup ramen.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like this will work.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inorganic! It's inedible!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Akihisa, I just made too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely didn't go out of my way for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Himeji?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Himeji brought one too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I don't think it's any good...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.88,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... I made this for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, I'd be really happy if you ate it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for an inquisition.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verdict is guilty. Death penalty.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even giving me a chance to speak this time!?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This isn't what you think!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lunch is, umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torture him first, then kill him.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right as rain. I can endure any \Nhardship in order to eat your cooking.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, shucks...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can interrupt us here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this looks awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.64,0:08:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I forgot the drinks. Hold on.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.46,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji is cute, smart, and great at cooking.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't deserve this.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, Yuuji!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.52,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man, we're just having a few bites-
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta get these guys to the nurse's-
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voyeur!?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food can't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It looks so good.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost got taken through the gate.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food is the reason why everyone fainted.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smelling it was bad enough...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akihisa...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you... Can you bring me a plate?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.82,0:10:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plate?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you might as well swallow\Nthe plate if you're eating the poison...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.63,0:10:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be fine if I swallow a plate...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, his cognitive ability is leaving him!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some drinks.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.03,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they got a little tired after eating, so they took a nap.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take a nap right after you eat you'll turn into a cow.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be a living cow than a dead human.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.34,0:10:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. What should I do?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to eat?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... it's just so beautiful, I can't bear to eat it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I imposing on you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm so glad you went to all this trouble for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.83,0:11:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you try your own cooking when you cook?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.32,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you'll get fat if you do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.89,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to be the first person to try it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fate is sealed.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are my super-ego and id agreeing with each other!?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.96,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Himeji. Could you get me a drink?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.65,0:11:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some oolong tea.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.05,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.69,0:12:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, I want you to listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.54,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spices have been used to cure poison since the olden days.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the refrigerator was invented,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were used as disinfectants in order to aid food preservation.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.75,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they say that a girl's love is the strongest spice in her cooking.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That means...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.65,0:12:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the spice named love to cure the poison.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a test!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to cast my life away for the sake of love.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.40,0:12:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the spice called love, no matter what the poison...!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love can't cure poison.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my hero, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RIP.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Yoshii?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got sleepy after eating.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll turn into a cow if you\Ntake a nap right after you eat.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Shimada?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all the time I spent on this...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have just been honest.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wasn't expecting that at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought Himeji could\Nactually be bad at something.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more hungry now...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen my sister?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.83,0:13:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I haven't...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to lunch?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some stuff happened that prevented me from retaining the calories.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.21,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've asked Minami for her lunch...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.70,0:14:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she made. Man, I really want to try it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki, the boxed-
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch together, Sissy!{fucking sissy}{srs}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu!?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking all over for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to try the special lunch I made just for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you here!?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class D doesn't have lessons today!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's Sunday as long as you're here!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come if you won't come, even if it's a school day!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does our school have so many retarded kids who can't think normally!?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy this fabulous moment with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look over there.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.03,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Stop following me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find an empty place to sit down and have lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.86,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Buzz off!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, she's just too shy.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sissy! Sissy!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.52,0:15:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I need to go find Aki...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge, Haiseiko!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No running in the halls.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki... Thank god.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure he takes it this time!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.99,0:15:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had two chicks make him lunch!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is inexcusable!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitors must be lynched.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitors must be lynched!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're getting the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, wait! Hang on! Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are out of your fucking minds!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge, Haru Urara!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.11,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No running in the halls.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're outside right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had just about enough for one day...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.04,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Stupid was playing with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't harass him too much, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aki.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had lunch yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess it could go either way...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.04,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hungry, umm...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.24,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Oshamanbe's specialty?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.64,0:17:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshamanbe's specialty is hair crabs.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.90,0:17:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.96,0:17:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here for some self-studying? It's Sunday, you know...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class F has supplementary lessons...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten lunch yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we eat lunch together?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda broke...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.79,0:17:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dearie me. Guess I'll have to pay for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch you later, Shimada.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we eat, let's come up with\Nsome strategies for the midterms.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Midterms?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hazuki, have you eaten lunch yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.23,0:18:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to since I was busy playing...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you need to get your vitamins.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna get big and tall?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was for Mr. Stupid...?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right. Like I'd cook something for that loser.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat it together then!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.65,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. I forgot that I still have lessons.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go home first?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll take the A set.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.35,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I get the B set since it's cheaper?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fukuhara.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't open this.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you summon your Being to help me open it?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Being...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.61,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were KIA are assigned supplementary lessons!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! I still haven't had anything to eat!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a dumbass.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.40,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a cutiepie.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to dig in.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk! That dumbass!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the biggest greatest hugest jerk in the world!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell would make lunch for him!?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.55,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to throw that away?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.87,0:21:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhh...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.87,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are starving people in Haiti, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you waste food, global warming will kill us all.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.72,0:21:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And karma will come for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.26,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh, I guess you can consider this recycling in an environmental sense...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.07,0:21:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that we need to take great care with how we use nonrenewable resources.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want it?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it then.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to cherish your resources-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.44,0:22:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question five:
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.09,0:23:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of the sport that requires a map and compass to reach a checkpoint?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RPG!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.19,0:23:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that would be your answer.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Maps and\NTreasures and Striker Sigma V.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.53,0:23:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on your test.
