Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:12.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HF1DEEB&}Just who are we letting grow up on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.29,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFF3BA&}Meeting someone else is the easy way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.95,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HEBD5FE&}I knew what I would say before they even asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.49,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HB1FFB2&}Do I look lovestruck enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.72,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HC9E4FF&}I'm not gonna lose my cool, love's at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.75,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCAC7FF&}Study! Study! Study! It keeps me up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.39,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFC9EB&}I've got a genius inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.97,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HA0E6FF&}It'd be great if my dreams came true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.22,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD6C3CB&}because I don't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.83,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD5CDFF&}Perfect area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HCDFFDC&}I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:02:00.11,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFFED3&}I can hear your voice from the perfect area ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.42,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HE8D4FF&}Fly! I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:07.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HBBECFF&}Yeah, that's me, the person you just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:08.64,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFCABF&}Are we still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.82,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HABFFC7&}I flunked our friendship test, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.14,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&H889DF8&}No! I'll take it again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.25,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFD8BF&}Come on, gimme another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:21.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HFFEBBF&}Something better awaits us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:28.08,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\c&HD7C3FD&}A better life awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.14,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:14.46,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&H9BBAFF&}Never, never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:15.79,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}One more chance! One more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:16.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\be1}{\an8\c&HFFC7C4&}Never give up!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.86,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}It's a time of peace now that school's out.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.96,0:22:24.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HC45007&}If I were to describe her, she's a real angel!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}Then came a notice that shattered my fun.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.67,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H9100FE&}It said I had to stay afterschool! It's like hell!!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.08,0:22:33.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}I was talking about it with my friends, and I said,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.09,0:22:36.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H0FF606&}"No way anyone's that stupid!!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.14,0:22:40.06,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}But deep inside me,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.19,0:22:42.56,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}I was shouting out,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.77,0:22:44.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H0000BC&}"I AM THAT STUPID!"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.44,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}That sign in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.65,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}that says "Monthly"...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.01,0:22:56.14,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H3300AE&\c&H000000&}I always thought that was the company's name.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.79,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.77,0:23:02.50,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Stupidity's a character! A real man!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.78,0:23:05.43,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&HA23500&}Our common sense is the lack thereof!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}We don't need rules in our fucking world!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H1F009B&}Eat steak out every night, overthrow the mass!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.92,0:23:17.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Take a look, the sun that rose from the west is setting back down!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.94,0:23:21.00,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Run home, it's almost dinner!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.66,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H99A000&}Let's get home!
